put thick makeups on me,

680
00:39:21,479 --> 00:39:22,600
I can't be a vase.

681
00:39:22,600 --> 00:39:25,640
I think you still haven't
understand the situation now.

682
00:39:25,920 --> 00:39:27,360
I'll get straight to the point.

683
00:39:27,759 --> 00:39:29,440
I don't care who you are.

684
00:39:29,600 --> 00:39:32,640
I just need you to be within my reach.

685
00:39:33,719 --> 00:39:35,039
Just like this tool.

686
00:39:35,880 --> 00:39:37,719
It's for the best if it works well.

687
00:39:37,880 --> 00:39:40,039
If it doesn't, I still have to use it.

688
00:39:40,279 --> 00:39:41,640
But it must be you.

689
