this is only a job.

691
00:39:45,920 --> 00:39:47,600
You don't need to think too much.

692
00:39:47,799 --> 00:39:48,920
Just follow my orders.

693
00:39:49,440 --> 00:39:50,719
I don't understand.

694
00:39:50,840 --> 00:39:52,640
Why must it be me?

695
00:39:53,120 --> 00:39:54,680
You don't need to know that.

696
00:39:55,440 --> 00:39:58,999
What you need to do now is
to memorise everything I gave you.

697
00:39:59,120 --> 00:40:01,120
I will test you tomorrow.

698
00:40:01,279 --> 00:40:03,160
If you're lazy about it,

699
00:40:03,759 --> 00:40:07,200
